styles.name: header_theme
styles.value:
.d-ui-widget-header,.ui-widget-header,.d-rte-panes>.d-menu.toolbar,.d-button {background-image: none,-webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0% #e2514d),color-stop(100% #d44946));background-image: none,-webkit-linear-gradient(top,#e2514d 0%,#d44946 100%);background-image: none,-moz-linear-gradient(top,#e2514d 0%,#d44946 100%);background-image: none,-o-linear-gradient(top,#e2514d 0%,#d44946 100%);background-image: none,-ms-linear-gradient(top,#e2514d 0%,#d44946 100%);background-image: none,linear-gradient(to bottom,#e2514d 0%,#d44946 100%);filter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient(startColorstr='#e2514d', endColorstr='#d44946',GradientType=0 );}
.d-ui-widget-header, .d-ui-widget-header > a,.ui-widget-header,.ui-widget-header>a,.d-rte-panes>.d-menu.toolbar,.d-button {color:#ffffff;}

styles.name: hover_states_theme
styles.value:
.d-ui-widget.d-state-hover,.d-ui-widget-header.d-state-hover,.d-item.d-state-hover,.d-node-content>.d-state-hover,.ui-state-hover {background-image: none,-webkit-gradient(linear, left top, left bottom, color-stop(0% #0cc1ee),color-stop(100% #049acd));background-image: none,-webkit-linear-gradient(top,#0cc1ee 0%,#049acd 100%);background-image: none,-moz-linear-gradient(top,#0cc1ee 0%,#049acd 100%);background-image: none,-o-linear-gradient(top,#0cc1ee 0%,#049acd 100%);background-image: none,-ms-linear-gradient(top,#0cc1ee 0%,#049acd 100%);background-image: none,linear-gradient(to bottom,#0cc1ee 0%,#049acd 100%);filter: progid:DXImageTransform.Microsoft.gradient(startColorstr='#0cc1ee', endColorstr='#049acd',GradientType=0 );}
.d-ui-widget.d-state-hover,.d-ui-widget-header.d-state-hover,.d-ui-widget-header.d-state-hover>a,.d-item.d-state-hover,.d-node-content>.d-state-hover,.ui-state-hover,.ui-state-hover>a {color:#ffffff;}
